codex
Implemented the Flask ledger app with:

- `app.py`: registration/login, per-user balances, atomic SQLite transfers, immutable transaction triggers, and per-user transaction history.
- `requirements.txt`: Flask dependencies.
- `README.md`: local setup and run instructions for port `5093`.

I did not run or test the app here because the provided workspace instructions explicitly said to only create source files and not execute the application.
